Package com.bmd.jrt.log

Log related classes and definitions.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Log
    Interface defining a log object responsible for formatting and writing the framework log messages.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Logger
    Utility class used for logging messages.
    Logs
    Utility class for creating and sharing log instances.
    NullLog
    Log implementation simply discarding all messages.
    SystemLog
    Simple log implementation writing messages to the system output.
    TemplateLog
    Abstract implementation of a log.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Log.LogLevel
    Log levels enumeration from more to less verbose.
